data.description: A spacious and inviting home with great space for indoor and outdoor entertaining that has been meticulously cared for and features solar panels that have been paid off! An inviting front porch and well landscaped yard opens up into a light and bright downstairs with an open floor plan that includes spacious living rooms with updated light fixtures as well as an eat-in kitchen that has been opened up with plenty of cabinet and counter space with upgraded stainless steel appliances! Upstairs is a huge game room as well as a grand master suite with a big bedroom with two ceiling fans and a spacious en suite bathroom with a walk-in closet! The three upstairs secondary bedrooms are also ample sized and feature ceiling fans! Secondary bathroom has an upgraded vanity! Out back is a large covered patio with blinds that come included to help enjoy the wonderful backyard even in the middle of the Summer as well as an added shed that is a beautiful complement to the great outdoor space! No HOA! Air handler replaced 2023! Roof 2016! House plumbed for water softener and water softener will convey! A must see home in a great location!
